	$LF
	"I drop in at the department store before going to the mayor's office. 
	$LF
	"I sell off a plastic bat for $40 and withdraw $50. 
	$LF
	"I purchase three loaves of bread for $30x3 in the fourth floor, and Pippi uses one loaf. 
	$LF
	"You will lose 16 frames if you stayed having stopped when you repeat the opening and shutting of the menu.
	$LF
	"I get $100 from the mayor and say goodbye to Pippi and meet her again in her house and have a boy return her bread crumb. 
	$LF
	"You can go to the broken world by using this bread crumb.
	$LF
